<strong>Location:</strong> Boston, Massachusetts, USA<br />
<strong>Security Protocol:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Agents are to arrive at Boston Harbor on December 17 to collect the crate. The crate is to be reported as lost cargo to anyone that inquires about it and amnestics are to be used when necessary.</span><br />
<strong>Note:</strong> No crates have manifested since December 17, 2002. Anomaly has been deemed neutralized and archived.</p>
<p><strong>Unexplained Location UE-139584</strong><br />
<strong>Description</strong> A 424,074&#160;km² area encompassing the entirety of the state of California as well as the town of ██████████, New Jersey in which calling the phone number &quot;867-5309&quot; will result in cardiac arrest exactly 7 days later. This anomaly is not known to have occurred at any time earlier than █████ ██th, 1997.<br />
